---
title: Sugar Shack Beef and Apple Burgers with Maple-Mustard Dressed Salad
description: This sugar shack-inspired meal features savoury beef burgers topped with caramelized apples and gooey white cheddar. Crisp mixed greens get tossed with toasted almonds, sweet baby tomatoes and a maple-mustard dressing for a tasty and balanced side.
